                            Solar technology has advanced dramatically, with sleek, efficient panels that can be
                            seamlessly integrated into roofing systems. Tesla's Solar Roof and similar products are
                            revolutionizing how we think about renewable energy in residential design.
                        </p>

                        <h3>Smart Home Systems</h3>

