                            Intelligent home automation systems now allow homeowners to monitor and optimize energy
                            usage in real-time, learning from patterns and automatically adjusting to maximize efficiency
                            without sacrificing comfort.
                        </p>

                        <h2>The Economic Benefits of Sustainable Design</h2>

